title: Astrodesigns Crafting Cardstock, 12" x 12", 65 lb/176 gsm, Bright White, 70 Sheets (91522)
description: This Astrodesigns Bright White Cardstock is the perfect canvas to any scrapbook page, craft project, greeting card and more! This pack contains 70 sheets to ensure you have enough on hand for all your creative needs. Plus, it’s lignin and acid-free so your creations won’t yellow over time. Perfect for scrapbooking enthusiasts and crafters alike, the 12" x 12" cardstock is compatible with electronic cutting machines so you can design intricate letters and shapes, greeting cards, posters, and more! Just create, score, cut or print!
